text: Jorge Celedón also known as Jorgito Celedón is a Colombian musician and singer of vallenato music. Celedón was one of the backup singers for the vallenato group Binomio de Oro de America who joined after the death of Rafael Orozco Maestre. In 1998, he decided to create his own vallenato group and teamed with accordionist Jimmy Zambrano. ==See also== *Carlos Vives *Patricia Teherán *Binomio de Oro de America *Rafael Escalona *Fanny Lú *Diomedes Díaz *Alci Acosta Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian musicians Category:Colombian singers en:Jorge Celedón
